## 4. WORKING AGREEMENTS FOR ANY AI/AGENT LOADING THIS FILE

- Treat Salesforce as truth. n8n is the brain. Heymarket/Aircall/Gmail are hands.
- Never propose a new SaaS without justifying why the existing stack can't carry it.
- Never propose a cadence step without specifying: source, day offset, channel, persona, message intent, exit condition.
- Always state compliance impact when touching SMS.
- Always specify how the kill switch is honored at every new step.
- When in doubt, ship the cheaper, faster version and instrument it.
